tip.text: Location is key , in the morning it's bustling with food and office crowd . The rooms are great for short term travellers .
Beautiful interior , gets packed but well worth the wait . Portions are large so be sure to keep space as everything on the menu is delectable !
This sums up what I miss ! My mornings with beautiful breakfast . Soft shell crab , fresh avocado & everything else on the menu .
Buy the beans, the house blend is such a must do for brewing it at home . try the agave & pepper latte and be sure to enjoy some quiet time in the right corner .
Bring it on , this cosy restaurant threw by surprise . The food was so good that we ate almost everything. Go crazy and order the chicken butt
Salads ! Portions are huge and they are a great lunch spot for girlfriends .

tip.text: I could do the self pampering daily , I truly enjoyed the special combo treatments . Note to travellers , do pick up the massage balm. Worth it
The food selection was amazing . We had to do second rounds on the steak as it was grilled to perfection !
Central location to legoland and the service apartments are new with good room size . Even the basic studio was adequate  for a single traveller . Only thing to note that food is not accessible .
Ramadhan buffet was delicious , with a hint of fine dining . The spread of choices is not about the amount of food but making sure each dish is done well . The desserts had an assortment , yummy !
Crimson is a one stop resort , location for families and those wanting to stay in to enjoy doing nothing . The restaurants have great food and 24 room service .
They have beautiful freshly baked good , coffee ( latte ) is always spot on . Go for the chocolate croissant !
A cosy accommodation, true to it's name . Hidden and tucked away . We had the 3 bedroom villa and an amazing view . The food is the best ! Service above satisfactory .

tip.text: It was a surprise stop over because as soon as you get in . The space opens up to a beautiful dining area . Great cocktails !

Everything was amazing . From our view , the starters and the mains. Great place to share plates and enjoy a good company . Dessert well try it all ! Enjoyed my chocolate mousse with a hint of chili .
Perfect hideout on a hot day , beautiful local interpretation of Bali food .
Everything was great . From the interior , the food . Chicken was cooked to perfection & the beef tartare was delectable . The drinks were slightly watered down due to too much ice .
Got a shocked when my eggs were almost hard boiled and the amount of oil & chilli floating looks more like an Asam pedas dish . Despite returning the dish , it came back oiler ....
Sunsets gazing for their special for 2 cocktails and canapés at 7pm . Sit out the beautiful lawn and enjoy the sea breeze .
Great pitstop hotel near bugis for that quick traveller . Modern minimal interior
A great way to start the morning , come in early ! And enjoy the company of cats . The food is mediocre

Hands down , delicious smoothie bowls

Freddo coffee and a place to spend the afternoon .
My feel good breakfast spot when I want to have a throwback European brunch . Great pastries and service .
Coffee is the best , brewed with love . The avocado is great and the caramel crepe cake !
